descriptionHtml:
Hello everyone im skull19972 and this is my mod number 6
SKYRIM MORE NPCS :

as you know i hate retextures so this mod is not a retex it dont change the oroginal npcs and it dont interface anything

This mod add some new npcs in Whiterun Winterhold Windelhelm Solitude Markarth Riften Falkreath Dawnstar Morthal 
dont worry it dont interface anything and it dont change the original npcs

it add some new npcs some of them are followers 
some of them just talking eating drinking
and some of them give you quests 
in every single city i did add new 10 npcs 
see this video and see the pictures

Soon i will add in my second version more quests because i did just add 15 new quests for now 3 big quests and 12 little quests
soon i will add more than that 
Enjoy!!!! by your freind skull19972
